Lables is defined pr pod, under the metadata section, in a key value format.

[img[k8s_labels.png]]

```yaml
metadata:
  name: simple-webapp
  labels:
    app: App1
    function: Front-end
```

[img[k8s_selector.png]]

```bash
kubectl get pods --selector app=App1
```

which is used by selectors


to create labels on a replicaset

[img[k8s_labels_replicaset.png]]

```bash
kubectl get pods --show-labels
kubectl get pods -l env=dev --no-headers | wc -l
```
